    "body": "Quick recap on the difficulty bomb: as discussed in [meeting 49](https://github.com/ethereum/pm/blob/master/All%20Core%20Devs%20Meetings/Meeting%2049.md):\r\n\r\n- Block times will begin to increase in Jan\r\n- Expected to reach 30s block times in May\r\n- Could be as early as early April if hashpower declines ~20-25%\r\n- Will hit faster than last year\r\n\r\nIt [looks like](https://etherscan.io/chart/blocktime) block times have just begun to tick up. Since the math was done it appears that hash power has come down by about 20%, so my best forecast at the moment is that we'd hit 30s block times in late April.",
